cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper discusses the relationship between neural networks and kernel methods, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also touches on optimization techniques, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and the use of neural networks in control systems, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
